reviews.review_text: This is an amazing recording For the last three years, I've been collecting, almost exclusively, the best audiences available, and which I can find in circulation. I had never heard, nor was I aware of the existence of these two recordings (Frost 82.10.09, also) . . . which doesn't mean much. The point is that these folks hit the sweet spot for sure and the recordings are, as noted below, "stellar." As was the mix at both shows. All instruments and vocals present and evenly balanced. These are real gems, and I am so grateful for the efforts of all who made it possible to bring these two recordings into wide circulation. You've made an old(-ish) Head very happy. Get these shows now. Five stars for the recording, because I'm going to love the music anyway . . .

Great show One of my all-time favorites

Sailor-Saint is Bobby at his best

The thin man spits!
